      "text": "On April 9, 1956, [REDACTED] was interviewed con-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "cerning her sighting of an unusual object about dawn April 6,",
      "status": "image_matched"
