      "text": "1956, while driving on Route 1 near Henderson, North Carolina,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "with her fiance, [REDACTED] Jr., an employee of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "[REDACTED] [REDACTED] was interviewed for additional",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "details in this matter on April 12, 1956, by Supervisor [REDACTED]",
