      "text": "from [REDACTED] to Mr. Nichols prior to being questioned for any",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "other details which might be of assistance to the Air Force in this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "matter. She advised she had seen the object for only a few seconds",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "that it was still dark when she observed it, although it was near",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "daylight on April 6, 1956. She stated when daylight came she",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "attempted to try to be cloudy and it started raining approxi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
