      "text": "recalled the object had approached their car on the driver's",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "side from straight ahead at a height which she thought to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "less than 25 feet. She was unable to estimate the speed of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "the object. She described it as being oval shaped, being very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
